{"tw": {"3436370": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "消滅！馬賽克！", "steam_appid": 3436370, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 故事</h2><br>在一個多種族和平共存的世界裡。某天，天上突然出現了裂縫，碰的一聲天空出現了個漆黑的大洞，從洞裡射出了許多魔法粒子打向了人們。被打到的人們衣服出現了異變，變得一塊一塊的就像馬賽克一樣。為了解救她們，少女魔法使與她的使魔登場了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 玩法</h2><br>擊出能量球來消滅馬賽克！只需要使用滑鼠就可以遊玩，左右移動來控制魔杖，還能按下右鍵蓄集魔力，蓄滿魔力後點擊左鍵可以發射雷魔法！<br>把所有的馬賽克消除乾淨吧！小心不要漏接能量球傷到自己！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 道具</h2><br>有時候破壞馬賽克磚會掉落魔法道具，蒐集這些好用的道具來消滅馬賽克吧！不過要小心可能會有負面效果的道具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 強化系統</h2><br>消滅馬賽克的途中主角也越來越強了，利用這些技能點數來精通各種屬性的魔法吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 豐富的角色</h2><br>世界各地都有需要主角拯救的可愛冒險者，快來剝光...我是說消滅這10位可憐冒險者身上的馬賽克吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/cd40aa4003122b7267fc588a1b5fd34f.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 黑影模式</h2><br>只是剝光不太夠?全裸後被魔物襲擊的冒險者們又被馬賽克纏上了！必須把馬賽克清理乾淨才行！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Boss關卡</h2><br>CG不會動太無趣了？除了靜態的關卡還有動態的Boss關卡！不只CG會動，還能獲得更多的技能點數！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 畫廊</h2><br>在畫廊裡有各種功能可以讓你更好地欣賞CG！除了關卡內容，破關時剩餘心數越多還能解鎖更多的CG圖！<br>一共有80張以上的靜態CG和5個動態CG以及更多的差分等著大家來欣賞！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 故事</h2><br>在一個多種族和平共存的世界裡。某天，天上突然出現了裂縫，碰的一聲天空出現了個漆黑的大洞，從洞裡射出了許多魔法粒子打向了人們。被打到的人們衣服出現了異變，變得一塊一塊的就像馬賽克一樣。為了解救她們，少女魔法使與她的使魔登場了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.poster.avif?t=1770781