ts/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 畫廊</h2><br>在畫廊裡有各種功能可以讓你更好地欣賞CG！除了關卡內容，破關時剩餘心數越多還能解鎖更多的CG圖！<br>一共有80張以上的靜態CG和5個動態CG以及更多的差分等著大家來欣賞！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "short_description": "這是一款消除爽感滿滿，角色動態精緻的奇幻風格的打磚塊遊戲。各式各樣的冒險者們衣服因為詛咒變成馬賽克了！快利用各種屬性的魔法來消滅這些馬賽克(以及他們的衣服)吧！", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/56c895c1f518971644909107a1ab6beebc296d46/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1770781540", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/56a1505500a800c67367352137615f36d17d12ab/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1770781540", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/56a1505500a800c67367352137615f36d17d12ab/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1770781540", "website": "https://playmeow.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> WIN10/XP<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 1.2 GHz<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9 compatible graphics card<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> WIN10/XP<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 1.2 GHz<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9 compatible graphics card<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["悠悠幽靈工作室"], "publishers": ["Playmeow", "Playmeow News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 10200, "final": 10200, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 102"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 11 月 18 日"}}}}, "us": {"3436370": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Destroy! Mosaic!", "steam_appid": 3436370, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Story</h2><br>In a world where many races live together peacefully. One day, a crack appeared in the sky, and with a loud bang, the crack turned into a large black hole, from which many magical particles shot out and hit people. The clothes of those who got hit changed and became like a mosaic. To save them, a young witch and her familiar appeared.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/650ad6d2db8261e0dbf3b8df2e226d1a.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Gameplay</h2><br>Hit the energy balls to destroy the mosaic! Use your mouse to play, move your wand left and right to control it, right click to charge magic power and left click to fire thunder magic when you've charged up your magic power!<br>Clear all the mosaics! Be careful not to miss the energy ball and hurt yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/28ca9637066ce79324bce1a036b16293.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Items</h2><br>Sometimes breaking mosaic tiles will drop magic items, collect those useful tools to destroy the mosaic! But be careful! Some magic items may have negative effects.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/595eb13486e57254aa4a8e5d38617c10.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Skill Enhancement System</h2><br>On your adventure to destroy the mosaic, the protagonist will grow stronger. Use these skill points to become proficient in various magic elements!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/406882721d96f5590d0471dc431ab39c.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Lots of Characters</h2><br>There are cute adventurers all over the world who need the protagonist to save them. Come and strip... I mean, eliminate the mosaic on those 10 poor adventurers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/cd40aa4003122b7267fc588a1b5fd34f.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Black Shadow mode</h2><br>Stripping naked isn’t enough? The naked adventurers are now attacked by monsters and got cursed with mosaic AGAIN!! The mosaic must be cleansed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/05d03fe62da14e7064e33bf49e162e02.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Boss levels</h2><br>Unanimated CGs feels a bit lackluster? Aside from regular levels, there are also boss levels with animated CGs! Not only that the CGs are animated, you also get to earn more skill points!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.webm?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/f31652cd0d46a3651d6e5486d357f6b7.mp4?t=1770781540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• Gallery</h2><br>&quot;There are various features in the gallery to help you better “enjoy” the CGs! In addition to the level content, the more heart points you have left when clearing a level, the more CGs you'll unlock! With over 80 CGs, 5 animated CGs, and many more variants, there's plenty for you to enjoy!&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.poster.avif?t=1770781540\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436370/extras/31875891623f2b961155cf4a5948c162.webm?t=1770